WEBVTT

00:04:30.020 --> 00:04:32.616
might seem like
a significant undertaking --

00:04:33.770 --> 00:04:36.436
and believe me, it very much was,
in the short term --

00:04:36.854 --> 00:04:38.966
it was nonetheless
having a positive effect

00:04:38.990 --> 00:04:41.846
on the way that I approached
everything else in my life.

00:04:42.711 --> 00:04:45.315
Not only did it transform
my ability to problem-solve,

00:04:45.339 --> 00:04:47.758
but I also felt I became more pragmatic,

00:04:48.912 --> 00:04:51.222
less sensitive to hindrances,

00:04:51.246 --> 00:04:52.869
in some cases, more patient,

00:04:53.943 --> 00:04:56.720
and magically transformed
people's abilities

00:04:56.744 --> 00:04:58.879
to offer me their seats
on public transport.

00:04:58.903 --> 00:05:00.798
(Laughter)